    12249 [label="ChooseALicense:\nHow to apply this license:\nCreate a text file (typically named LICENSE or LICENSE.txt) in the root of your\nsource code and copy the text of the license into the file. Do not replace the\ncopyright notice (year, author), which refers to the license itself, not the\nlicensed project."
